{"tid":1431956,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"不要叫「光復香港，時代革命」，試著叫「打倒共產黨」","createTime":"2019-08-08T06:09:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T06:09:44.000Z","uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fe1b69d62f94733ebc4fc9b77f7997a81f7c0287","tid":1431956,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:09:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不要叫「光復香港，時代革命」，試著叫「打倒共產黨」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n民間調查發現，不少中立淺黃市民都<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔明白</span></span></strong>「光復香港，時代革命」嘅意思，口號亦唔夠傳神，做唔到一針見血，鼓勵唔到香港人團結同拉攏中立人士加入。<br />\n<br />\n應直接叫<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>「打倒共產黨」</strong></span></span>，，簡單易明針對問題核心，亦可以勾起市民對於共產黨恐懼<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n順便提醒下班藍絲廢老當日係因為逃避邊個嘅魔爪先要落嚟香港"}]}